ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectBarry Devolin ** MP Travel **
PrecisOrder authorizing Mr. BARRY DEVOLIN, Member of Parliament for the constituency of HALIBURTON-KAWARTHA LAKES-BROCK, Ontario, to undertake travel to the REPUBLIC OF KOREA for several days in late August and September 2014 in order to discuss the benefits of the CANADA-KOREA FREE TRADE AGREEMENT with members of the National Assembly of the Republic of Korea.
